2011-03-21 10:10:27,067 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;main&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; ERROR org.apache.pig.tools.grunt.Grunt - ERROR 0: Line 1:23 duplicated alias in schema: u&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Unit test passed.&lt;br/&gt;
